{
    "key": 225,
    "texts": [
        "<p>你检查了这个挂锁。它很老旧，也不是特别坚固。附近有很多金属碎片可以当作简易开锁器使用。但你真的会开锁吗？</p>",
        "[guide-start]",
        "<p>进行一次“锁匠”检定。这一次检定你可以将技能值加倍。</p>",
        "[guide-end]"
    ],
    "interactions": [
        {
            "text": "锁匠检定-技能值加倍",
            "action": "action_check",
            "param": {
                "key": "locksmith",
                "isSkill": true,
                "level": "value"
            },
            "show": ["flag_check_unfinished", "!flag_punish_dice"]
        },
        {
            "text": "锁匠检定-技能值加倍-惩罚骰x1",
            "action": "action_check",
            "param": {
                "key": "locksmith",
                "isSkill": true,
                "level": "value",
                "bonus": -1
            },
            "show": ["flag_check_unfinished", "flag_punish_dice"]
        }
    ],
    "options": [
        { "key": 0, "text": "继续", "show": "flag_check_passed" },
        { "key": 1, "text": "继续", "show": "flag_check_failed" }
    ],
    "onload": [
        { "action": "action_double_skill_value", "param": "locksmith" },
        { "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "locksmith", "level": "value" } }
    ],
    "onleave": [
        { "action": "action_half_skill_value", "param": "locksmith" },
        { "action": "action_set_highlight", "param": { "key": "locksmith", "level": "none" } }
    ]
}